				<td colspan="2"><span>Actually, stay out of Fear right now.  They added a Berzerker epic mob with an AE mez of very high radius who patrols near the zone-in.  One tactic I have seen used successfully is to have a necro dot himself before zoning in so if he gets mezzed, it will be broken by the dot each tick.  The necro (and SKs could do this well too) then pulls the nasty mob away while the rest of the raid gets on with the break.
<br />

<br />
Beware.  A monk guildee of mine often solos in Fear and got a rude awakening.
<br />

<br />
Calli</span></td>
