Next day I nipped in -- having cleverly avoided being a part of the original silliness -- just to see whether Ireblind was still camping the zone.  He was.  He started chasing me.
<br />

<br />
Now, MAYBE he isn't KOS and was just coming to give me a love hug and tell me what a special bard I am.
